The Granite Arcade holds Conclave-era correspondence referencing the Western Fold sanctum and condemned-labor transfers along Roc Road toward "the mountain academy."
Glasswash Fan obsidian and sulfur feed Midgaard's alchemical networks.
Bellspine crystal seismic monitoring is nominally the Wizard's Keep containment office's responsibility; no survey expedition has been funded in eleven years.
Ash Cult activity in the Ember Crown is classified as frontier religious variance.

